White voluntarily gives up the bishop pair while temporarily grabbing a pawn. Black will soon restore material, but White will have fixed the pawn structure in a particular way (obtaining the so-called 'Carlsbad structure'), and they are banking on this being to their advantage. } Nxg5 { Capturing the bishop on g5 and remaining down a pawn for now is best, as Black has a concrete way of restoring material equality soon. } 
