This game is unlike many of the other games shown in this section. The reason I wanted to share it is that, if we play the Grünfeld enough times, then we will for sure find ourselves having gone wrong out of the opening and facing a losing position. However, the Grünfeld is an opening that offers so much tactical dynamism that you can keep practical chances alive until the end, even against high-level opposition.

